videos.description: Seth Curry fires a pass to an open Ben Simmons who flushes it home forcing a Washington timeout.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Curry catches Wizards napping, whips pass to Simmons for dunk) 2021/05/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Curry catches Wizards napping, whips pass to Simmons for dunk

videos.description: Joel Embiid pins Daniel Gafford under the basket and muscles in the easy layup.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Embiid bodies Gafford in the post for easy layup) 2021/05/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Embiid bodies Gafford in the post for easy layup

videos.description: Raul Neto's floater falls off the rim, but Daniel Gafford is there to clean it up with a dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Gafford emphatically follows miss with a dunk) 2021/05/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gafford emphatically follows miss with a dunk

videos.description: Russell Westbrook goes right at the retreating George Hill for the and-1 finish.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Westbrook goes right at Hill for and-1) 2021/05/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Westbrook goes right at Hill for and-1

videos.description: Joel Embiid knocks down the 3-pointer and tells the crowd to quiet down.
videos.headline: Embiid shushes crowd after 3

videos.description: Ben Simmons hits the floater over Russell Westbrook and runs back on defense giving the "too small" celebration.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Simmons hits Westbrook with the 'too small' celebration) 2021/05/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Simmons hits Westbrook with the 'too small' celebration

videos.description: Joel Embiid misses the dunk, then comes back and absolutely destroys the rim on an and-1 dunk a couple possessions later.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Embiid loves what he is hearing from the crowd after this slam) 2021/05/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Embiid loves what he is hearing from the crowd after this slam

videos.description: Russell Westbrook throws the pass through traffic to a running Daniel Gafford for the jam.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Russ threads needle to Gafford for slam) 2021/05/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Russ threads needle to Gafford for slam

videos.description: The Wizards send a double team to Joel Embiid, but it's no use as he knocks down the jumper.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Double team? No problem for Embiid) 2021/05/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Double team? No problem for Embiid

videos.description: Joel Embiid does it from outside and inside as he scores a playoff career-high 36 points, leading Philadelphia to a 3-0 series lead.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Embiid scores playoff career-high 36 in dominant Game 3 win) 2021/05/29 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Embiid scores playoff career-high 36 in dominant Game 3 win
